result.markdown: --- title: "Week 7: ARIMA models" --- ::: {.cell} ::: ## What you will learn this week * Stationarity and differencing * Random Walk Models ## Exercises (on your own or in tutorial) Complete Exercises 5-7, 10-15 from [Section 8.8 of the book](https://otexts.com/fpp3/expsmooth-exercises.html). ## Exercise solutions ## Pre-seminar activities Read [Sections 9.1-9.2 of the textbook](https://otexts.com/fpp3/arima.html) and watch all embedded videos. ## Assignments * [GA2](../assignments/G2.qmd) is due on Monday 14 April. * [IA3](../assignments/A3.qmd) is due on Monday 28 April. * [GA3](../assignments/G3.qmd) is due on Monday 05 May.
